      <title>两名 Ukrenergo 监事会成员因首席执行官被罢免而辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/two-ukrenergo-supervisory-board-members-quit-over-ceo-ouster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰电力公司监事会的两名独立成员宣布辞职，以抗议罢免乌克兰电网运营商负责人的“出于政治动机”的决定，并称此举危及了与欧洲合作伙伴的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/two-ukrenergo-supervisory-board-members-quit-over-ceo-ouster</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 12:47:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希腊银行在升级后股价上涨，大幅削减 AT1 成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/greek-bank-slashes-at1-cost-as-it-rides-post-upgrade-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家希腊银行大幅削减了资本成本，凸显了在信用评级升级和人们对最具风险的银行债务的广泛需求下该国资产的上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/greek-bank-slashes-at1-cost-as-it-rides-post-upgrade-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 09:11:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>供应增加、需求疲软加剧悲观情绪，油价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在利比亚有望恢复供应的协议使交易员的注意力重新转向对全球原油需求低迷的担忧之后，油价暴跌 — 抹去了今年的涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-3</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 23:26:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
